Large-scale:
	- use a large number of data points
	- having a large customer base

Distributed:
	- use a large number of machines
	- having a large number of data centers across the world

Design-patter:
	- common problem
	- common solution
	ex:
		Youtube content publishing an notify subscribers
		Netflix content publishing an notify subscribers
		Instagram content publishing an notify followers
		- common problem: publish content and notify subscribers
		- common solution: publisher and subscriber model

LLD:
	- requirement gathering
	- use cases diagram
	- class diagram with relationships
	- convert class diagram to Model
	- implement code
		- OOPS + SOLID principles + Design pattern
	- design services/controllers
